casebody.data:
No. 11-6711. Angeliki Papadimitriou, Petitioner v. John Papadimitriou. 565 U.S. 1056, 132 S. Ct. 797,

181 L. Ed. 2d 479,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8646. November 28, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied. Petitioner is allowed until December 19, 2011, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 417 Md. 502, 10 A.3d 1181.
